thread.title: Deputies investigate possible sexual battery outside Disney World entertainment complex
thread.title_full: Deputies investigate possible sexual battery outside Disney World entertainment complex - Winnipeg Free Press

author: The Associated Press
title: Deputies investigate possible sexual battery outside Disney World entertainment complex
text:
LAKE BUENA VISTA, Fla. - Deputies are investigating a possible sexual battery after a woman was found naked and disoriented outside Walt Disney World's restaurant and entertainment complex last week.
Detectives said Wednesday that the woman was found by a security guard last Thursday in shrubbery outside Disney Springs, which used to be known as Downtown Disney.
The woman told detectives she had no recollection of how she got there, and that if any sexual activity took place, it wasn't consensual.
She says she had gone to the House of Blues music venue at Disney Springs with friends after drinking at her apartment.
She says she became separated from her friends and doesn't remember anything else.
